vibe main

yeet "vibez"

fr fr Test to validate floating-point output format parity
fr fr Ensures interpreter and compiled modes produce identical output
fr fr Expected: Compact floating-point format (3.5, not 3.500000)

slay main_character() {
    vibez.spill("=== Floating Point Format Test ===")
    
    sus simple_float meal = 3.5
    sus calc_result meal = 1.75
    
    vibez.spill("Simple float:")
    vibez.spill(simple_float)
    
    vibez.spill("Calculated result:")
    vibez.spill(calc_result)
    
    vibez.spill("=== Test Complete ===")
}
